ified by the software.

                                In terms of inputs, we plan to offer the trained algorithm a photo of an unidentified plant with the hope that the algorithm will return the same image, annotated or labeled. Similarly, we hope that the returned image and plant profile will contain data relevant to the plant regarding its edibility, location, and other uses.

